<div id="content">
	<h1 class="documentFirstHeading"><span id="parent-fieldname-title">Scientific Success </span></h1>
<p><img src="/_asset/image/journal-banner-short.jpeg" alt="journal banner_short" /></p>
<div class="columns">
<h3>Scientific Success of the Institute</h3>
<p>The work of the Institute has developed very quickly since 1989.&nbsp; Notable successes in the field of immunology, haematopoiesis stem cell biology, infectious diseases and human genetics are set out below. Our work has had major impact in understanding disease mechanisms and how to diagnose and treat both common (e.g. diabetes, rheumatoid arthritis, multiple sclerosis, malaria, thalassaemia, leukaemia, cystic fibrosis, meningitis and AIDS) and rare (a wide range of developmental disorders including neurological diseases and abnormal facial development) human diseases.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><img class="centre" src="/_asset/image/nanodrop1.jpeg/fit/460/768" alt="nanodrop1" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3>Major Scientific Breakthroughs by WIMM-Based Scientists</h3>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
